## Forbidden Practices

**DO NOT create these files:**
- ❌ TODO.md, NOTES.md, SESSION_*.md

**DO NOT write these comments:**
- ❌ `// TODO:`, `# FIXME:`, `/* HACK: */`

**USE IdlerGear instead:**
- ✅ `idlergear task create "..." --label tech-debt`
- ✅ `idlergear note create "..."`

